<doc id="32189" wikidata="Q2431804" url="?curid=32189" title="Underground railway">
<text>Underground railway may refer to:

*The Underground Railroad, a network of clandestine routes by which African slaves in the 19th century United States attempted to escape
*Rapid transit, a high capacity urban railway that uses tunnels
* Mine railway, an underground rail system used in mining

==See also==
*Underground Railroad (disambiguation)</text><links>
