* Cole, Dave, and James X. Dempsey. &quot;Terrorism and the Constitution: Sacrificing Civil Liberties in the Name of National Security&quot;. 2nd ed. New York: W. W. Norton &amp; Co., 2002. . (Full discussion of prior legislative history of the Act, going back more than ten years.)
